{% block content %}
{{
  case_study_header(
    title='Facebook Watch SG Guide',
    tags=['Comms', 'Design']
  )
}}

<section class="hero">
  <img
    draggable="false"
    src="/assets/img/case-studies/fb-watch/hero_background.jpg"
    alt="For this Facebook Watch Party, We Brought the Hype." />
</section>

<section class="intro">
  <div class="cs-container">
    <div class="cs-container__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column intro__left">
        <p data-aos="fade-up">
          Facebook Watch is a premier video-on-demand destination offering loads of original content, minus the pesky subscription fees. For their upcoming media showcase in Singapore, our clients wanted to highlight the best and brightest of what Facebook Watch had to offer.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column intro__right">
        <img
          class="intro__image"
          data-aos="fade-up"
          src="/assets/img/case-studies/fb-watch/intro_image.gif" alt="FB Watch intro image">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="project-popcorn">
  <div class="cs-container">
    <div class="cs-container__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column"></div>
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column project-popcorn__text__column">
        <p data-aos="fade-up"
        class="project-popcorn__text">
          Our job was to create an event guidebook that would get people genuinely excited about Facebook Watch, positioning it as the best TV invention since… popcorn. And with the date looming dangerously close, there was no time to lose.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="project-cover">
  <div class="cs-container">
    <div class="cs-container__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column project-cover__left">
                <img
                        data-aos="fade-up"
                        class="project-cover__image__left"
                        src="/assets/img/case-studies/fb-watch/cover_image_left.gif"
                        alt="Facebook Watch Singapore Guide"
                />
      </div>
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column project-cover__right">
        <img
                data-aos="fade-up" draggable="false"
                class="project-cover__image__right"
                src="/assets/img/case-studies/fb-watch/cover_image_right.png"
                alt="Watch Whatever, Whenever, Wherever">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="project-whenever">
  <div class="cs-container">
    <div class="cs-container__row project-whenever__images__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column project-whenever__left">
        <img
                data-aos="fade-up" draggable="false"
                class="project-whenever__image__flower"
                src="/assets/img/case-studies/fb-watch/whenever_image_flower.png">
        <p data-aos="fade-up">
          <strong>Whatever, Whenever, Wherever:</strong><br>
          That was the mantra that guided us to create this series of illustrations on the cover. Of course, we wouldn’t recommend watching when you’re in the driver’s seat. That’s just irresponsible.
        </p>
        <img
                data-aos="fade-up" draggable="false"
                class="project-whenever__image__emojis"
                src="/assets/img/case-studies/fb-watch/whenever_emojis.gif">
      </div>
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column project-whenever__right"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="project-creators">
  <div class="cs-container">

    <div class="cs-container__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column project-creators__text">
        <p data-aos="fade-up">
          With loads of creators to feature, we cheekily combined the themes from the different Facebook Watch shows in the graphics throughout the guide.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
    <div class="cs-container__row project-creators__images__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column project-creators__images__column">
        <img
                data-aos="fade-up" draggable="false"
                class="project-creators__image__left "
                src="/assets/img/case-studies/fb-watch/creators_image_left.png">
      </div>
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column project-creators__images__column">
        <img
                data-aos="fade-up" draggable="false"
                class="project-creators__image__right"
                src="/assets/img/case-studies/fb-watch/creators_image_right.gif">
        <img
                data-aos="fade-up" draggable="false"
                class="project-creators__image__emojis"
                src="/assets/img/case-studies/fb-watch/creators_image_emojis.png">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cs-container__row project-creators__cupcakes_row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column project-creators__cupcakes__column">
        <img
                class="project-creators__image__cupcakes animate_image"
                src="/assets/img/case-studies/fb-watch/creators_image_cupcakes.png">
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<section class="project-OGS">
  <div class="cs-container">
    <div class="cs-container__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column project-OGS__top__left" data-aos="fade-up" draggable="false"></div>
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column project-OGS__top__right" data-aos="fade-up" draggable="false">
        <p class="project-OGS__top__right__text" data-aos="fade-up">
          To accurately capture the essence of each show, we took some time to tune in and explore the stories behind them. This was especially interesting for us when it came to the homegrown winners of the Facebook Creator Lab, Our Grandfather Story and Share Food Singapore. Food and nostalgia? Two subjects we hold very close to our hearts.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cs-container__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column project-OGS__bottom__left" data-aos="fade-up" draggable="false">
        <p class="project-OGS__bottom__left__text" data-aos="fade-up" draggable="false">
          As storytellers and viewers ourselves, we didn’t want to slap a generic description on each show and call it a day. Our guide had to compel the attendees to get on Facebook Watch right after the event ended, and start their own Watch Party.
        </p>
        <img data-aos="fade-up" draggable="false"
             src="/assets/img/case-studies/fb-watch/OGS_image_crew.gif"
             alt="Storytellers FB Watch Party"
             class="project-OGS__bottom__left__image">
      </div>
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column project-OGS__bottom__right" data-aos="fade-up" draggable="false"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="project-einvite">
  <div class="cs-container">
    <div class="cs-container__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column project-einvite__text">
        <p data-aos="fade-up">
          Once the guide was out, it was a cinch to adapt the master creative to an e-invite for the event.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cs-container__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column project-einvite__left">
        <img data-aos="fade-up" draggable="false"
             class="project-einvite__image__left"
             src="/assets/img/case-studies/fb-watch/einvite_image_left.png">
      </div>

      <div class="col-md cs-container__column project-einvite__middle">
        <img data-aos="fade-up" draggable="false"
           class="project-einvite__image__middle"
           src="/assets/img/case-studies/fb-watch/einvite_image_middle.gif">
      </div>

      <div class="col-md cs-container__column project-einvite__right">
        <img data-aos="fade-up" draggable="false"
             class="project-einvite__image__right"
             src="/assets/img/case-studies/fb-watch/einvite_image_right.png">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="project-end">
  <div class="cs-container">

    <div class="cs-container__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column">
        <img
             class="project-end__emojis animate_image"
             src="/assets/img/case-studies/fb-watch/end_image_emojis.png">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="cs-container__row project-end__content__row">
      <div class="col-md cs-container__column project-end__left">
        <img data-aos="fade-up" draggable="false"
             class="project-end__image__left"
             src="/assets/img/case-studies/fb-watch/end_image_showcase.gif">
      </div>

      <div class="col-md cs-container__column project-end__right">
        <p data-aos="fade-up" class="project-end__text">
          The showcase was a runaway success, with the guide setting the stage for a fantastic presentation from each of the featured guests.
          <br><br>
          For us, it was an extra-special event, being in the audience while having access to all that insider knowledge.
          <br><br>
          If there was a real-life Like button, we’d have been the first ones to click on it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

